{"tid":164851,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"越南沙壩Sapa 河內行程求推介","createTime":"2017-03-21T03:09:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-25T06:05:35.000Z","uid":52819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b982a35007e3797dacedf4fce03885df30ab0bc3","tid":164851,"uid":52819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T03:09:13.000Z","msg":"想問下有無去過Sapa沙壩既巴打係去到先Join local tour?  <br />\n<br />\n價錢質素 如何？  <br />\n<br />\n因為小弟接近夜晚12點先到河內機場，預計會係機場附近酒店訓一晚，再直上Sapa，所以參加唔到一定要係河內市中心上車既團 eg sinh cafe 果啲tour  要另外坐車去到再join  <br />\n<br />\n另外沙壩有無咩係必去既地方？   <br />\n<br />\n感謝 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05fa4e46840d7baf5a302c4eda355e0ec15a8716","tid":164851,"uid":52819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T03:26:58.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"96cc95543ed165e31a45cb7ceb1db3d485a966b5","tid":164851,"uid":52819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T03:39:12.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"fb963b70d13e6b996231f57233aa778ccd866899","tid":164851,"uid":23416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T03:41:25.000Z","msg":"上網搞簽證    上網訂埋去沙霸個程  <br />\n帶夠衫   一定要背包     唔好去下龍灣  d海鮮仲貴撚過香港  <br />\n全部the north fake  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56cec10d46b9e20527e2e87f59c4481861e6c0f3","tid":164851,"uid":23416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T03:43:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問下有無去過Sapa沙壩既巴打係去到先Join local tour?  <br />\n<br />\n價錢質素 如何？  <br />\n<br />\n因為小弟接近夜晚12點先到河內機場，預計會係機場附近酒店訓一晚，再直上Sapa，所以參加唔到一定要係河內市中心上車既團 eg sinh cafe 果啲tour  要另外坐車去到再join  <br />\n<br />\n另外沙壩有無咩係必去既地方？   <br />\n<br />\n感謝 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n落到地   見到d民族嬸嬸就會sell你行山  睇梯田  <br />\n可以行山兩日一夜/欖車上山頂"},{"pid":"f19fe73f0fe46b24dbd084e6294e7cc78a67686a","tid":164851,"uid":52819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T03:58:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上網搞簽證    上網訂埋去沙霸個程  <br />\n帶夠衫   一定要背包     唔好去下龍灣  d海鮮仲貴撚過香港  <br />\n全部the north fake  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上網見到有大巴 由機場去老街 大約$80 HKD<br />\n<br />\n諗住到時再坐Public bus上Sapa<br />\n<br />\n仲有無其他方法？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n下龍個個都話一般 應該不了"},{"pid":"54f60845f5a8d14f78393e48b41fe74d601b81ed","tid":164851,"uid":52819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T04:00:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想問下有無去過Sapa沙壩既巴打係去到先Join local tour?  <br />\n<br />\n價錢質素 如何？  <br />\n<br />\n因為小弟接近夜晚12點先到河內機場，預計會係機場附近酒店訓一晚，再直上Sapa，所以參加唔到一定要係河內市中心上車既團 eg sinh cafe 果啲tour  要另外坐車去到再join  <br />\n<br />\n另外沙壩有無咩係必去既地方？   <br />\n<br />\n感謝 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n落到地   見到d民族嬸嬸就會sell你行山  睇梯田  <br />\n可以行山兩日一夜/欖車上山頂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n落地join local tour個價同上網買定分別大唔大？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31469babc2cafafaddb029f6129953e241b239f5","tid":164851,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T04:14:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://sapaexpress.com/en\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsapaexpress.com%2Fen&d=Au6C6jYmoXJsWFOyr%2BboKP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=35e8ccc3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://sapaexpress.com/en</a><br />\n巴士好舒服<br />\n其實你主要係去sapa?<br />\n你可以河口離境，去埋元陽梯田。"},{"pid":"cb66cb135785acd00bb8eea82fa78e8f20f97492","tid":164851,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T04:17:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想問下有無去過Sapa沙壩既巴打係去到先Join local tour?  <br />\n<br />\n價錢質素 如何？  <br />\n<br />\n因為小弟接近夜晚12點先到河內機場，預計會係機場附近酒店訓一晚，再直上Sapa，所以參加唔到一定要係河內市中心上車既團 eg sinh cafe 果啲tour  要另外坐車去到再join  <br />\n<br />\n另外沙壩有無咩係必去既地方？   <br />\n<br />\n感謝 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n落到地   見到d民族嬸嬸就會sell你行山  睇梯田  <br />\n可以行山兩日一夜/欖車上山頂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n落地join local tour個價同上網買定分別大唔大？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nD人話sapa好多tour<br />\n但我個日去到好大雨<br />\n問自己間酒店。好鬼貴。只可包1人團。<br />\n因為太大雨。所以冇搵其實tour。自己鳩行"},{"pid":"01fe6a4597ccb43a167efb067230c5165ad46c55","tid":164851,"uid":35803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T04:21:47.000Z","msg":"Sapa好似無鋪頭travel agency, 可能要靠酒店同上面巴打講既民族嬸嬸<br />\n唔建議上網book，價錢可以差好遠<br />\n我係河內Sinh cafe 當地報3日夜火車團<br />\n主要行village, 訓一晚sapa市中心酒店，行一日山住一晚民宿，風景一流<br />\n但膳食真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我只係要求粗茶淡飯姐，行左成朝山你俾個即食面我做lunch<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n河內報團可以選擇Rose travel, 下龍灣團我報佢<br />\n個staff非常好服務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6214eb5ad84fa864c3284729506132d6799cd6e4","tid":164851,"uid":8833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T04:54:24.000Z","msg":"黎緊3月尾我都去河內<br />\n但我河內&mdash;下龍灣&mdash;南定<br />\n<br />\n下龍灣就網上格完價，揀左一間3星船USD88<br />\nSapa我朋友無興趣<br />\n但我超想去，最後ban左<br />\n今次我地3人就機場搭USD15去酒店<br />\n車都book左"},{"pid":"10d06465f1ef48447f523241c5f0e67f49a6651d","tid":164851,"uid":52819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T05:42:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://sapaexpress.com/en\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsapaexpress.com%2Fen&d=Au6C6jYmoXJsWFOyr%2BboKP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=35e8ccc3\" target=\"_blank\">http://sapaexpress.com/en</a><br />\n巴士好舒服<br />\n其實你主要係去sapa?<br />\n你可以河口離境，去埋元陽梯田。</blockquote><br />\nSapa 3日2夜+河內市hea幾日<br />\n<br />\n咁近大陸都有諗過過埋境 但都係下次先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e34faa28529e059935e8c406050316d1fe467030","tid":164851,"uid":52819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T05:45:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Sapa好似無鋪頭travel agency, 可能要靠酒店同上面巴打講既民族嬸嬸<br />\n唔建議上網book，價錢可以差好遠<br />\n我係河內Sinh cafe 當地報3日夜火車團<br />\n主要行village, 訓一晚sapa市中心酒店，行一日山住一晚民宿，風景一流<br />\n但膳食真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我只係要求粗茶淡飯姐，行左成朝山你俾個即食面我做lunch<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n河內報團可以選擇Rose travel, 下龍灣團我報佢<br />\n個staff非常好服務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁一於去到先再搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n希望唔好搵到位太伏既tour guide<br />\n<br />\n另外想問其實Sapa景點之間坐車/搵的士難唔難？其實唔跟團會唔會好難去到晒咁多景點？<br />\n<br />\nLunch公仔麵笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  河內市中心周圍行算"},{"pid":"27aeb15ed7be7533a8e545221cd399e4538a230b","tid":164851,"uid":35803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T05:45:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>黎緊3月尾我都去河內<br />\n但我河內&mdash;下龍灣&mdash;南定<br />\n<br />\n下龍灣就網上格完價，揀左一間3星船USD88<br />\nSapa我朋友無興趣<br />\n但我超想去，最後ban左<br />\n今次我地3人就機場搭USD15去酒店<br />\n車都book左</blockquote><br />\n我當地報都好似差唔多價錢，3星船訓一晚<br />\n唔好咁傻報一日下龍團，搭車去哂d時間<br />\n下龍灣其實無講到咁差，有時間可以一戰<br />\n上甲板望住d山哂太陽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n岩洞就把鬼既，下午玩下kayaking, 夜晚上甲板啤酒睇星<br />\n<br />\nBtw3星船其實夠做，仲有機會同鬼妹同房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24bd8cbe7bc230e8c55d4db5a4affa6991c46740","tid":164851,"uid":52819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T05:45:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>黎緊3月尾我都去河內<br />\n但我河內&mdash;下龍灣&mdash;南定<br />\n<br />\n下龍灣就網上格完價，揀左一間3星船USD88<br />\nSapa我朋友無興趣<br />\n但我超想去，最後ban左<br />\n今次我地3人就機場搭USD15去酒店<br />\n車都book左</blockquote><br />\n分開玩幾日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3935019df7da643bb32f14cc54ff862b477cb7c9","tid":164851,"uid":23416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T05:51:19.000Z","msg":"仲有d的士佬好西   成日呃鳩你錢"},{"pid":"1cf68f6e6d3d53a76c544c9e1fef15a367b5c772","tid":164851,"uid":35803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T05:54:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Sapa好似無鋪頭travel agency, 可能要靠酒店同上面巴打講既民族嬸嬸<br />\n唔建議上網book，價錢可以差好遠<br />\n我係河內Sinh cafe 當地報3日夜火車團<br />\n主要行village, 訓一晚sapa市中心酒店，行一日山住一晚民宿，風景一流<br />\n但膳食真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我只係要求粗茶淡飯姐，行左成朝山你俾個即食面我做lunch<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n河內報團可以選擇Rose travel, 下龍灣團我報佢<br />\n個staff非常好服務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁一於去到先再搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n希望唔好搵到位太伏既tour guide<br />\n<br />\n另外想問其實Sapa景點之間坐車/搵的士難唔難？其實唔跟團會唔會好難去到晒咁多景點？<br />\n<br />\nLunch公仔麵笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  河內市中心周圍行算</blockquote><br />\n同行澳洲仔食個公仔面食到lam lam利，湯都飲埋，我笑而不語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n理論上入到sapa市中心，所有地方都係靠行<br />\n唯一要交通既，係sapa火車站入市中心果程<br />\n除非你唔住民宿，就咁睇睇個village, 唔係就河內報團or sapa搵嬸嬸"},{"pid":"89fc223aace5471faa9a570c0702477d63cf0ea3","tid":164851,"uid":8833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T05:55:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>黎緊3月尾我都去河內<br />\n但我河內&mdash;下龍灣&mdash;南定<br />\n<br />\n下龍灣就網上格完價，揀左一間3星船USD88<br />\nSapa我朋友無興趣<br />\n但我超想去，最後ban左<br />\n今次我地3人就機場搭USD15去酒店<br />\n車都book左</blockquote><br />\n我當地報都好似差唔多價錢，3星船訓一晚<br />\n唔好咁傻報一日下龍團，搭車去哂d時間<br />\n下龍灣其實無講到咁差，有時間可以一戰<br />\n上甲板望住d山哂太陽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n岩洞就把鬼既，下午玩下kayaking, 夜晚上甲板啤酒睇星<br />\n<br />\nBtw3星船其實夠做，仲有機會同鬼妹同房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n話曬第一次去越北<br />\n想去晒當地既景點無悔<br />\n但可惜班老友唔願行程太密想輕鬆遊<br />\n<br />\n所以無去sapa<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"367f7f7dcc0ca48894eee024e66ba0b67cf531ef","tid":164851,"uid":8833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T05:56:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>黎緊3月尾我都去河內<br />\n但我河內&mdash;下龍灣&mdash;南定<br />\n<br />\n下龍灣就網上格完價，揀左一間3星船USD88<br />\nSapa我朋友無興趣<br />\n但我超想去，最後ban左<br />\n今次我地3人就機場搭USD15去酒店<br />\n車都book左</blockquote><br />\n分開玩幾日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打河內點玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有咩景點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"378224733114e8fb3170d321a8cd9239f8bf5e6a","tid":164851,"uid":23416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T05:57:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>黎緊3月尾我都去河內<br />\n但我河內&mdash;下龍灣&mdash;南定<br />\n<br />\n下龍灣就網上格完價，揀左一間3星船USD88<br />\nSapa我朋友無興趣<br />\n但我超想去，最後ban左<br />\n今次我地3人就機場搭USD15去酒店<br />\n車都book左</blockquote><br />\n分開玩幾日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/face